Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.20,0:01:07.50,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}自分らしさってなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.26,0:01:10.75,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}「人とは違う」で差をつけろ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.99,0:01:13.23,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}コンビニの雑誌コーナー
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.73,0:01:16.62,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}表紙にふとして書いてあった
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.68,0:01:18.96,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}自分らしさってなんだ　
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.43,0:01:21.98,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}子供の頃は気にもせず
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.47,0:01:24.94,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}気に入らなければ怒って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.97,0:01:27.86,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}好きなものを好きだと言って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.94,0:01:31.03,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}僕らは変わってく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.03,0:01:33.90,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}守りたいものが変わってゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.90,0:01:36.65,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}理解されない宝物から
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.72,0:01:39.39,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}理解されるための建前へ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.39,0:01:44.92,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}大人になるほど　後悔する生き物になる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.93,0:01:47.54,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}でもね　それでもね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.94,0:01:51.87,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}見えるものがあるんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.53,0:01:58.96,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}だから僕は僕らしく　そして君は君らしくって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.96,0:02:04.95,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}初めから　探すようなものではないんだと思うんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.95,0:02:10.22,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}僕は君じゃないし　君も僕じゃないから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.23,0:02:13.09,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}すれ違う　手をつなぐ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.14,0:02:17.70,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}そこには愛だって生まれる　そういうもんさ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.87,0:02:21.60,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}自分らしさってなんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.66,0:02:27.72,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}変えられない　大切があるから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.12,0:02:31.47,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}変わりゆく生活が　正しい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.10,0:20:28.55,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}You held out a small hand
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.68,0:20:34.44,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}Smiling like to you it was so natural
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.02,0:20:39.61,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}It may have no meaning
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.84,0:20:45.38,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}but it is something I cannot do
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.71,0:20:51.45,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}You touched my hand without thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.45,0:20:55.24,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}but it was nice for me
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.17,0:21:03.56,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}All the time we believed
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.68,0:21:09.04,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}that the world was in our hands
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.23,0:21:11.94,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}We were wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.94,0:21:20.01,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}maybe it wasn't 'cause \Nyou're holding my hand now
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.01,0:21:25.63,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}At every moment
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.74,0:21:31.17,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}Everywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.27,0:21:36.50,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}I can believe, I can believe
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.83,0:21:41.68,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}When I'm holding your warm hand
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.74,0:21:49.05,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}your warm hand
